Title: Good Ol' Whatshisname
Plot: Mr. Krabs pits SpongeBob against Squidward in a work contest, promising the winner a fabulous prize. The challenge is to find out all of the customers' names. When they cover almost all of them, Squidward tries desperately to find out the name of a grumpy man.
Writer: Casey Alexander, Zeus Cervas, Richard Pursel
